Researchfields
1.Novelfunctionalmaterials
2.Interactionoftheexternalintensivefieldswithmatter
3.Micro-structuredfiber.

Selectedpublications
Since2000,Prof.Qiuhaspublishedmorethan50SCI-indexedpapersintheinternationaljournalssuchasAngew.Chem.,Phys.Rev.Lett.andAppl.Phys.Lett.,etc.Thesepapershavebeencitedformorethan500times.
